---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="GNC Financial privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[65ch] mx-auto px-5 md:px-10 prose text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-500 mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>GNC Financial ("we", "us", "our") is an accounting practice based at Suite 111, 33 Lexington Drive, Bella Vista NSW 2153. We are committed to protecting the privacy of our clients and website visitors in accordance with the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs) under the <em>Privacy Act 1988</em> (Cth).</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">2. Information we collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1 ml-4">
        <li>Name, email address, phone number, and postal address</li>
        <li>Tax file numbers and financial information (provided for the purpose of accounting services)</li>
        <li>Business details (ABN, ACN, business structure)</li>
        <li>Information submitted through our contact form</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">3. How we use your information</h2>
      <p>We use your personal information to:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1 ml-4">
        <li>Provide accounting, tax, and advisory services</li>
        <li>Respond to enquiries and booking requests</li>
        <li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations (including ATO requirements)</li>
        <li>Send relevant updates about tax deadlines or changes that affect you</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">4. How we protect your information</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable steps to protect personal information from misuse, loss, and unauthorised access. Financial data is stored in secure, access-controlled systems. We do not sell or rent personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">5. Third parties</h2>
      <p>We may share information with:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1 ml-4">
        <li>The Australian Taxation Office (as required for tax lodgments)</li>
        <li>ASIC (for company compliance matters)</li>
        <li>Cloud software providers (Xero, MYOB, QuickBooks) used to deliver our services</li>
        <li>Web3Forms (contact form submissions)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
      <p>This website does not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics at this time. If we add analytics in the future, this policy will be updated.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">7. Your rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information. To make a request, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@gncfinancial.com.au" class="text-accent-700 underline">admin@gncfinancial.com.au</a> or call <a href="tel:0284032770" class="text-accent-700 underline">02 8403 2770</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mt-10 mb-3">8. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>
